            &lt;q&gt;Working Backwards&lt;/q&gt;&lt;p&gt;Insights, Stories, and Secrets from Inside Amazon&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Author: Colin Bryar&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/figcaption&gt;
